1787:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            / (TS_CAL2_TEMP - TS_CAL1_TEMP)
1788:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL1   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
1789:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL1 (calibrated in factory)
1790:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL2   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
1791:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL2 (calibrated in factory)
1792:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve that calibration
