2078:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Stabilization time of measurement path to internal channel:
2079:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         After enabling internal paths, before starting ADC conversion,
