2486:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC trigger frequency mode.
2487:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   ADC trigger frequency mode must be set to low frequency when
2488:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         a duration is exceeded before ADC conversion start trigger event
2489:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         (between ADC enable and ADC conversion start trigger event
2490:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         or between two ADC conversion start trigger event).
2491:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Duration value: Refer to device datasheet, parameter "tIdle".
2492:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   When ADC trigger frequency mode is set to low frequency,
2493:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         some rearm cycles are inserted before performing ADC conversion
2494:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         start, inducing a delay of 2 ADC clock cycles.
2495:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Usage of ADC trigger frequency mode with ADC low power mode:
2496:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Low power mode auto wait: Only the first ADC conversion
2497:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           start trigger inserts the rearm delay.
2498:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Low power mode auto power-off: ADC trigger frequency mode
2499:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           is discarded.
