2824:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - Sequence direction: Unless specified in parameters, sequencer
2825:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from rank 1 to rank n).
