3593:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC continuous conversion mode on ADC group regular.
3594:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   Description of ADC continuous conversion mode:
