3633:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Set ADC group regular conversion data transfer: no transfer or
3634:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         transfer by DMA, and DMA requests mode.
3635:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If transfer by DMA selected, specifies the DMA requests
3636:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         mode:
3637:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         - Limited mode (One shot mode): DMA transfer requests are stopped
3638:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           when number of DMA data transfers (number of
3639:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           ADC conversions) is reached.
