3645:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   If ADC DMA requests mode is set to unlimited and DMA is set to
3646:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         mode non-circular:
3647:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         when DMA transfers size will be reached, DMA will stop transfers of
