4041:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *           - resolution: resolution is not limited (corresponds to
4042:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             ADC resolution configured).
