 499:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   * @brief  Initialize some features of ADC instance.
 500:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   * @note   These parameters have an impact on ADC scope: ADC instance.
 501:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         Refer to corresponding unitary functions into
 502:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         @ref ADC_LL_EF_Configuration_ADC_Instance .
 503:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   * @note   The setting of these parameters by function @ref LL_ADC_Init()
 504:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         is conditioned to ADC state:
 505:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         ADC instance must be disabled.
 506:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         This condition is applied to all ADC features, for efficiency
 507:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         and compatibility over all STM32 series. However, the different
 508:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         features can be set under different ADC state conditions
 509:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         (setting possible with ADC enabled without conversion on going,
 510:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         ADC enabled with conversion on going, ...)
 511:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         Each feature can be updated afterwards with a unitary function
 512:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         and potentially with ADC in a different state than disabled,
 513:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         refer to description of each function for setting
 514:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         conditioned to ADC state.
 515:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   * @note   After using this function, some other features must be configured
 516:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         using LL unitary functions.
 517:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *         The minimum configuration remaining to be done is:
 518:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *          - Set ADC group regular sequencer:
 519:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            Depending on the sequencer mode (refer to
 520:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerConfigurable() ):
 521:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            - map channel on the selected sequencer rank.
 522:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *              Refer to function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerRanks();
 523:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            - map channel on rank corresponding to channel number.
 524:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *              Refer to function @ref LL_ADC_REG_SetSequencerChannels();
 525:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *          - Set ADC channel sampling time
 526:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            Refer to function LL_ADC_SetSamplingTimeCommonChannels();
 527:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   *            Refer to function LL_ADC_SetChannelSamplingTime();
 528:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_ll_adc.c ****   * @param  ADCx ADC instance
